Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet,\Na wind-up doll, and a crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:07.86,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mystery-solving logic drenches the walls of dry hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case is the first original TV 2-parter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayor! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did last night's storm carry it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ryujin-Maru"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't that the boat that was lost 7 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:48.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was 1 billion yen in gold on that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be! Where did all the gold go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you suppose it turned up only now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fools! There is no curse! It's just a dumb superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:36.18,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Deputy Mayor of Shikishima\NGoro Kinoshita (53)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll land on Shikishima in 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We greatly appreciate your coming all the way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to give a lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it certainly is a long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear a ship that went missing with 1 billion yen in gold onboard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,recently turned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! People on the island think it's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the money never turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. We're not even sure there really was any onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mayor is just glad that the town has garnered a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ghost ship garnering attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inviting someone so famous is another way of gaining prestige!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My reputation extends this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of Japan knows about the great detective Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He works for a Tokyo travel agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to create a tour centered around the ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.96,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shikishima
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:18.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Welcome, Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a warm welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}! Thank you for coming all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.58,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mayor of Shikishima\NTakeo Mikami (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mayor Mikami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We welcome you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this lame guy really famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you would've been a lot cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Don't be rude to Daddy's guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a lovely daughter you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan. Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a weird name. Is that the trend in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.45,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mayor Mikami's Daughter\NSuzu Mikami (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Suzu Mikami! It looks like I'm a little older than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being with younger people is trendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the travel agent—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toto Travel Agency\NYasuo Uehara (44)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Uehara from Toto Travel Agency.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likewise! We'll help in any way\Nto bring tourists here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the ghost ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks. I'll look for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ship was on the ocean floor for years
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but only has barnacles on its underside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dummy! It's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Talk about unscientific...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:15.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Lighthouse Keeper\NKoji Hamada (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Great Detective Kogoro Mouri Lecture"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!\NThere's still time until the lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These cooked turban shells are delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, after the lecture,\NI'd like to ask for your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to find where the Ryujin-Maru sank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such perceptiveness!\NI think it sank near this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we just knew where,\Nwe could locate the missing gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if it were recovered, it wouldn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The government would come to collect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't we be entitled to 10% of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! No famous detective would ever go treasure hunting—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about 10% of the island's reward money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita! Give him the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened on a stormy night seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We received an SOS from the Ryujin-Maru about 1 km offshore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the signal disappeared as a rescue crew headed for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the next day, only the owner's body washed ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No debris was ever found, much less the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whose gold was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ship's owner's. He was going to be arrested for tax evasion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he converted his entire fortune into gold and was on his way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,out of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well! I, Kogoro Mouri, shall locate the gold for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this lecture thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he just gonna humiliate himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suigun{\i0} Artifact Museum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The general's armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There's so much rare stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's this island's cultural heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,400 years ago, the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} escaped here after being defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in a large battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the islanders wanted the reward money for their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and attacked the wounded {\i1}Suigun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They eventually drove them into a remote cave and killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Various bad things have occurred ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. So a shrine was built in the cave to quiet the {\i1}Suigun{\i0}'s spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aren't curses just superstitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many people who live near the cave\Nhave seen armor-clad ghosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and eerie groans can be heard coming from the cave's depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was about five years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when a university professor studying the {\i1}Suigun{\i0} visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ignored the islanders' warnings and went to examine the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But two or three nights later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that professor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was never confirmed, but he was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody dares go near that cave anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believing that in this day and age\Nis why you get laughed at!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy said the professor checked the cave but probably left
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'cause he didn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! I'll show you a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can sneak backstage from here!\NBest seats in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hamada, the lighthouse keeper. He's really weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hardly hangs out with anyone, and he always goes to that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you don't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI'm Hamada, the lighthouse keeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have the wrong person! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tear that face of yours off, Aoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, here is the peerless Detective Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he be all right drunk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He appears to be rather nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have him break the celebration ball in honor of his visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- What on earth?!\N- Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the curse! The {\i1}Suigun{\i0} curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:37.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah. That string was modified to ignite the gasoline inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The target being... the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In which case, the ones most suspect are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, who left out the back door,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:50.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the man he got in an argument with, Uehara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it have something to do with the ghost ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayor! What's the meaning of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only survived because I'm so well-trained!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies for getting you involved in such an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accident?! Someone clearly planned that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, sparks from a short circuit\Njust happened to ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a nearby gas container—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure you just don't want a police incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't gonna turn the gold over\Nif you found it, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you'd have no choice if the mainland police showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! You just need to keep quiet and find the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Defy me and there's no guarantee you'll leave the island unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't threaten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't take the ferry without my authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, take your time to think it over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we came to a pretty bad island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize. The mayor seems to only care about finding the gold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and turning the island into a tourist attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a selfish bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take you back to the mainland anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I can prepare a small fishing boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I refuse to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inadvisable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be harmed if you stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No self-respecting detective would dare run away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well said, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Hamada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the lighthouse keeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:17:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know; he's not from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came here a while after the Ryujin-Maru incident
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and said he was looking for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no one working the lighthouse, so he took that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Hamada do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I just thought he seemed strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:45.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude! You should thank me for following you late at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, we're not that close of friends yet—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uehara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So he was that person up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person was searching the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's gasoline. Yet there are no cars or motorcycles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:40.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So it was Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} who tried to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan! Don't run off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was he doing up here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it. There's nothing to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pointed at the mountains. They'd be boring to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:10.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange. A lighthouse telescope should be pointing out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this one is fixed toward the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Ryujin-Maru"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No question about it! Hamada{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} is connected to the Ryujin-Maru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's something\Nhe doesn't want investigated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so he tried to kill the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! The old man and Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to run with my sore butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?! I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad was attacked by a {\i1}Suigun{\i0} ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The alarm bell by the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They ring it whenever something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:20.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is some sort of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That detective killed Hamada, the lighthouse keeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check for yourself if you think we're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we arrived on the scene, the detective was unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the victim was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghosts got mad because\Nan outsider was poking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He would never do\nsomething like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But given the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.59,0:24:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghosts are mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:03.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:08.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, this was no suicide!\NIn which case, the killer is—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:15.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.03,0:24:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Gunshot Wound
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:22.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, the case takes an unexpected turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The culprit is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:24.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No, Genta, it's not!
